summary: This document is a summary of account balances and transactions for a Deutsche Bank account from March 1, 2015, to March 31, 2015. It details deposits, withdrawals, service charges, and interest payments, providing insight into the financial activities during this period.
keyFacts: The account had a beginning balance of $6,345.87 on March 1, 2015.
There were two preauthorized debit transactions of $50.00 each on March 16, 2015.
An interest payment of $1.07 was credited to the account on March 31, 2015.
The ending balance of the account as of March 31, 2015, was $6,246.94.
No service charges or overdraft fees were incurred during this statement period.
